        <div class="pp-modal-row"><div class="pp-modal-row__name">Very Good</div><div class="pp-modal-row__desc">Slight signs of use with no significant defects.</div></div>
        <div class="pp-modal-row"><div class="pp-modal-row__name">Excellent</div><div class="pp-modal-row__desc">Near-perfect condition with minimal visible wear.</div></div>
